## Description
Scientific name: [_Ligustrum lucidum_](https://www.gbif.org/species/3172297)
Genus: ligustrum
Family: oleaceae
Order: lamiales

## Position
Prefers a bright position, with direct sunlight at least part of the day.

## Watering
On hot days it needs a lot of water and must be watered thoroughly as soon as the soil gets dry. In Winter water less but take care not to let the rootball dry out completely.

